  <brief_title>Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of MPA in Stable Renal Transplant Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Pharmacokinetic and Pharmacodynamic Parameters in Renal Transplant Patients Receiving Mycophenolic Acid and Stable for at Least 3 Months</official_title>
