  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study of the pharmacokinetic and pharmacodynamic variability of mycophenolate mofetil in
      renal transplant patients already on long-term MMF treatment (at least 6 months
      post-transplant; at least 3 months in therapy).

      Study hypothesis: to investigate whether long-term MMF therapy alters IMPDH biological
      activity and if there are any correlations with the risk of AR.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
